parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. The knocking noise can indicate engine damage, which can lead to engine failure, oil leaks, and even engine fires.
symptoms: The engine makes a loud knocking or rattling sound
the check engine warning light is illuminated
the vehicle loses power or accelerates slowly
the vehicle goes into limp mode
the oil level is low
and the engine is burning oil.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The software update can cause the engine to malfunction, leading to loss of power, engine failure, and even engine fires.
symptoms: The check engine warning light is illuminated
the vehicle loses power or accelerates slowly
the vehicle goes into limp mode
and the engine makes a loud knocking or rattling sound.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Oil leaks and burning oil can cause engine damage, leading to engine failure, and even engine fires.
symptoms: The oil level is low
the engine is burning oil
and there is an oil leak.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering coupler can cause the steering wheel to jerk, vibrate, or lock up, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Clicking
popping
or grinding noise when turning the steering wheel
loose or vibrating steering wheel
difficulty turning the steering wheel
jerking or locking up of the steering wheel
loss of power steering assist.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Oil Consumption and Catalytic Converter Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive engine oil consumption can lead to engine failure, and catalytic converter issues can cause the vehicle to shut down, posing a safety risk to the driver and occupants.
symptoms: Engine burning oil excessively
constant need to add oil
engine failure
catalytic converter failure
vehicle shutting down
loss of power
difficulty starting the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical issues can cause the airbag light to malfunction, leading to a false sense of security, and can also affect the functionality of other safety features, posing a risk to the driver and occupants.
symptoms: Airbag light flashing or staying on
horn malfunctioning
radio turning on and off
buttons on the steering wheel not working
cruise control settings unreliable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the airbags not deploying in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbags do not deploy in an accident
the seatbelt light is illuminated
the horn and steering wheel buttons do not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to the airbags not deploying in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the light comes on and off intermittently
the light stays on after an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clockspring can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the airbags not deploying in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the horn and steering wheel buttons do not work
the airbag system is malfunctioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to catch fire, resulting in property damage and potential harm to occupants.
symptoms: Smoke coming from the charger port
flames erupting from the vehicle
electrical problems affecting the radio
gas gauge
lights
and traction
and the airbag light staying on consistently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose power and lead to accidents, potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake lights remaining on
engine turning on without pressing the brake pedal
and the vehicle skidding or losing power when braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, potentially resulting in accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine hesitation
stalling
or shutting off while driving
oil consumption
and the engine light coming on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy in the event of an accident, potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the lighting system can cause the vehicle to be less visible to other drivers, potentially resulting in accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power and lead to accidents, potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
